# Conventional commits

Use `<type>(<scope>): <description>`.

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `refactor`, `docs`, `style`, `perf`, `test`, `chore`.

Scopes: `backend`, `client`, `game`, `creator`, `curses`, `auth`, `ci`, `deps`, `config`.

One coherent change per commit; PRs should tell one reviewable story (Graphite stacks merge bottom-up).
